title: The Incredible Hulk - Compete Peter David Run (1987-1998 + Extra
description: Hulk SMASH! This torrent collects all of Peter David's amazing, lauded run on the Incredible Hulk, from issue #331 to #467. In addition, all subset issues from other comics are including with "B" lettering as appropriate.
